      <title>飓风贝丽尔逼近墨西哥，强度增强至三级</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/05/g-s1-8442/hurricane-beryl-strengthens-category-3-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风贝丽尔横扫加勒比海东部，造成严重破坏，至少 9 人死亡，周四晚间再次增强为 3 级飓风。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/05/g-s1-8442/hurricane-beryl-strengthens-category-3-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:11:48 GMT</pubDate>
