    <item>
      <title>筑巢的鸟类使得一些人无法使用空调</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/04/nx-s1-5022846/nesting-birds-are-preventing-some-people-from-being-able-to-use-their-a-c-units</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现在正值全国的筑巢季节，鸟类在空调机组内和周围安家。这尤其令人担忧，因为热穹顶和热浪席卷了美国许多地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/04/nx-s1-5022846/nesting-birds-are-preventing-some-people-from-being-able-to-use-their-a-c-units</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 22:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工党在历史性选举中获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/04/g-s1-8429/uk-labour-party-election-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党领袖基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将于当天晚些时候正式就任首相，在遭遇近一个世纪以来最惨痛失败不到五年后，他带领工党重新执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/04/g-s1-8429/uk-labour-party-election-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:52:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
